Package: rddsga
Title: Weighted Subgroup Analysis in Regression Discontinuity Designs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Alvaro", "Carril", email = "alvarocarril@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements inverse probability weighted (IPW) subgroup analysis for
    regression discontinuity (RD) designs. Fits a propensity score model for
    subgroup membership within the bandwidth, constructs IPW weights so that
    observed moderators are balanced across subgroups at the cutoff, and
    estimates per-subgroup RD effects and their difference via weighted local
    polynomial regression. Supports sharp and fuzzy RD designs, three kernel
    types, polynomial order selection, multiple weighting modes, common support
    trimming, and bootstrap inference (standard, block, and fixed first-stage).
